      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Mark Lefler</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/File:Marklefler.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/c/c0/Marklefler.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Marklefler.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Mark Lefler</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Mark Lefler</b>,<br />\nan American computer games and chess programmer. He is author of the computer chess program <a href=\"/Now\" title=\"Now\">Now</a> and along with <a href=\"/Jeff_Mallett\" title=\"Jeff Mallett\">Jeff Mallett</a> co-author of the <a href=\"/General_Game_Playing\" title=\"General Game Playing\">general game playing</a> program <a href=\"/Zillions_of_Games\" title=\"Zillions of Games\">Zillions of Games</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> as well a co-founder of the <i>Zillions Development Corporation</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. In October 2013, <a href=\"/Don_Dailey\" title=\"Don Dailey\">Don Dailey</a> introduced Mark Lefler as new member of the <a href=\"/Komodo\" title=\"Komodo\">Komodo</a> team <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\nMark graduated in 1981 with a BS degree in Engineering Science and Mechanics from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Virginia_Polytechnic_Institute_and_State_University\">Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University</a>. His non-computer interests include performing magic, music, and gaming <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> . Mark served as member of the <a href=\"/Who%27s_Who\" title=\"Who&#39;s Who\">Secretariat</a> of <a href=\"/ICGA_Investigations\" title=\"ICGA Investigations\">ICGA Investigations</a> in 2011, and superseded <a href=\"/R%C3%A9mi_Coulom\" title=\"Rémi Coulom\">Rémi Coulom</a> as Programmers Representative of the <a href=\"/ICGA\" title=\"ICGA\">ICGA</a> in November 2011. Mark founded this <a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Chess Programming Wiki</a> on October 26, 2007 <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> . \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Photos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#WCCC_1999\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">WCCC 1999</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#WCCC_2016\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">WCCC 2016</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#1990_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1990 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#What_links_here.3F\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">What links here?</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos\">Photos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mark_Lefler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Photos\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"WCCC_1999\">WCCC 1999</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mark_Lefler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: WCCC 1999\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tnone\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:642px;\"><a href=\"http://wwwcs.uni-paderborn.de/%7Ewccc99/links/gallery.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/8/8d/IkarusNow.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:IkarusNow.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/Munjong_Kolss\" title=\"Munjong Kolss\">Munjong</a> &amp; <a href=\"/Muntsin_Kolss\" title=\"Muntsin Kolss\">Muntsin Kolss</a> and Mark Lefler, <a href=\"/WCCC_1999\" title=\"WCCC 1999\">WCCC 1999</a>: <a href=\"/Ikarus\" title=\"Ikarus\">Ikarus</a> - <a href=\"/Now\" title=\"Now\">Now</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"WCCC_2016\">WCCC 2016</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mark_Lefler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: WCCC 2016\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tnone\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:642px;\"><a href=\"https://icga.leidenuniv.nl/?page_id=1930\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/7/7a/WCCC2016_TeamKomodoShannonTrophy.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"424\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:WCCC2016_TeamKomodoShannonTrophy.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/WCCC_2016\" title=\"WCCC 2016\">WCCC 2016</a>, <a href=\"/Komodo\" title=\"Komodo\">Komodo</a> team <a href=\"/Erdogan_G%C3%BCnes\" title=\"Erdogan Günes\">Erdogan Günes</a> and Mark Lefler with the <a href=\"/Shannon_Trophy\" title=\"Shannon Trophy\">Shannon Trophy</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mark_Lefler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mark Lefler</a> (<b>1991</b>). <i>1991 World Microcomputer Chess Championship</i>. <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Reports\" title=\"Computer Chess Reports\">Computer Chess Reports</a> 1991, Vol. 2, No. 1, pp. 2-3&#160;» <a href=\"/WMCCC_1991\" title=\"WMCCC 1991\">WMCCC 1991</a></li></ul>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mark_Lefler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span>