uter_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, August 02, 2006&#160;» <a href=\"/Persistent_Hash_Table\" title=\"Persistent Hash Table\">Persistent Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=5377\">Piece Cooperation and Penalties</a> by mjlef, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, August 14, 2006&#160;» <a href=\"/Material_Tables\" title=\"Material Tables\">Material Tables</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2007</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=6066\">Reducing King Moves?</a> by mjlef, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, January 03, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Reductions\" title=\"Reductions\">Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=6072\">Castling legality check</a> by mjlef, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, January 04, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Castling\" title=\"Castling\">Castling</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=6421\">How good is your SEE?</a> by mjlef, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, April 24, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=14333\">Revisiting Check Extensions</a> by Mark Lefler, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 07, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Check_Extensions\" title=\"Check Extensions\">Check Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tal