d Pawn\">Backward Pawn</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2009</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27387\">Relative Piece Values</a> by Mark Lefler, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 09, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Point_Value\" title=\"Point Value\">Point Value</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27616\">Testing of Kaufman Material Values</a> by Mark Lefler, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 25, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Point_Value\" title=\"Point Value\">Point Value</a>, <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27842\">Rook Pair Penalty, Knight Pair Penalty, Having a Pawn Bonus</a> by Mark Lefler, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 11, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=28167\">Side to Move Bonus - does it help?</a> by Mark Lefler, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 29, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Tempo\" title=\"Tempo\">Tempo</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=28266\">No PVS at low depths?</a> by Mark Lefler, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 05, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30211\">Singular Extensions revisited</a> by Mark Lefler, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 19, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Singular_Extensions\" title=\"Singular Extensions\">Singular Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ww